media/2018/07/DSCF6728.jpg?resolution=412,2.625";s:5:"thumb";s:123:"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSVGFZnhgJoSHsnWPrSRCvQdgD2EPGfqH6oewo3P8hHJTLdl1Dz5xU4hMlfugyKaEzPNSY";s:8:"filetype";s:3:"jpg";s:5:"width";i:1333;s:6:"height";i:2000;s:6:"source";s:61:"https://expeditionportal.com/field-tested-helinox-chair-zero/";s:6:"domain";s:20:"expeditionportal.com";}i:19;a:11:{s:7:"keyword";s:23:"helinox chair zero test";s:4:"slug";s:23:"helinox-chair-zero-test";s:5:"title";s:63:"Helinox Chair Zero Review The Best Backpacking Chair 99boulders";s:3:"alt";s:10:"99boulders";s:3:"url";s:81:"https://www.99boulders.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/DSC00615-e1569459584886.jpg";s:5:"thumb";s:123:"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQm4MbNhVLSIcE7_z0p51M4YAJAlNfDHmmuGxvvJlYzwdEBjCenXvxS2VRhpJDx1qEg7f8";s:8:"filetype";s:3:"jpg";s:5:"width";i:467;s:6:"height";i:700;s:6:"source";s:52:"https://www.99boulders.com/helinox-chair-zero-review";s:6:"domain";s:18:"www.99boulders.com";}i:20;a:11:{s:7:"keyword";s:23:"helinox chair zero test";s:4:"slug";s:23:"helinox-chair-zero-test";s:5:"title";s:41:"Helinox Chair Zero Definitive Review 2021";s:3:"alt";s:17:"top notch outdoor";s:3:"url";s:91:"https://topnotchoutdoor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Helinox-Chair-Zero-Feature-Image.jpg";s:5:"thumb";s:90:"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRjZWjIYBRioTK0zak6rXr5NIs7yaWB8Npuhw";s:8:"filetype";s:3:"jpg";s:5:"width";i:500;s:6:"height";i:800;s:6:"source";s:47:"https://topnotchoutdoor.com/helinox-chair-zero/";s:6:"domain";s:19:"topnotchoutdoor.com";}}s:9:"sentences";a:69:{i:0;s:171:"The Helinox Chair Zero stands out in our test as one of the most comfortable and lightest of the tent-style models and it was barely beat out for our Editors Choice award.";i:1;s:117:"For the highly weight-conscious users who want an elevated chair we believe there isnt a better option in our review.";i:2;s:30:"Der Unterscheid zum Chair One.";i:3;s:88:"Groß sind die Unterschiede zwischen dem Chair Zero und dem Chair One von Helinox nicht.";i:4;s:63:"Die Sitzhöhe des Chair Zero ist um wenige Zentimeter geringer.";i:5;s:166:"Auch ist das Gestänge insgesamt kürzer was dazu führt dass der Zero gegenüber dem Chair One kompakter und leichter ist und sich wohl eher für Wanderungen eignet.";i:6;s:116:"The Helinox Chair Zero is a lightweight durable and compact chair that you can take with you on your next adventure.";i:7;s:131:"With a weight of just 17oz 048kg the Chair Zero is perfect for those who like to travel light and fast without sacrificing comfort.";i:8;s:45:"Get light comfy and tiny with the Chair Zero.";i:9;s:160:"Weighing just over a pound the Helinox Chair Zero features a remarkably low weight incredible packability and durable construction unmatched by its competition.";i:10;s:116:"After some rigorous field testing of sitting around we found the Chair Zeros performance lived up to its reputation.";i:11;s:35:"What type of camping chair is this.";i:12;s:85:"This Chair Zero won the Gold Award at the 2017 Friedrichshafen OutDoor Industry show.";i:13;s:137:"In the decision of the jury I read that Helinox lightweight camping chairs started a whole new trendThe Chair Zero weighs just 460 grams.";i:14;s:53:"This is amazingly light for such a comfortable chair.";i:15;s:37:"The Helinox Chair Zero has two parts.";i:16;s:37:"A cloth sling and a pole-based frame.";i:17;s:36:"To pack roll the pole into the seat.";i:18;s:185:"The seat has four reinforced corners that fit over the ends of the poles and this end up is printed on one side of the seat so you can orient it properly when attaching it to the frame.";i:19;s:48:"Features and Benefits of the Helinox Chair Zero.";i:20;s:140:"This compact camping and backpacking chair weighs just 11 pounds and packs smaller than a bottle of water measures 4 x 4 x 14 inches packed.";i:21;s:134:"Chair frame is constructed from advanced proprietary aluminum alloy to provide maximum strength which holds a person up to 260 pounds.";i:22;s:97:"Our Chair Zero measures 25 in high x 185 in wide assembled and holds up to 265 lbs 120 kilograms.";i:23;s:55:"Its also the smallest and lightest chair Helinox makes.";i:24;s:126:"While the seat depth is the same as our popular Chair One the Zeros seat is slightly more narrow and sits lower to the ground.";i:25;s:29:"Helinox Chair Zero tech spec.";i:26;s:38:"The Helinox Chair Zero is lightweight.";i:27;s:64:"An easy to carry 490g about the same as a small bottle of water.";i:28;s:92:"It can take weights of up to 120kg or 18st 8lb and its the lightest chair that Helinox make.";i:29;s:87:"When packed away it measures 76 x 76 x 356 cm and it also comes with a 5 year warranty.";i:30;s:55:"135 x 4 weighs in at 11 pounds and supports 265 pounds.";i:31;s:57:"135 x 525 weighs in at 22 pounds and supports 320 pounds.";i:32;s:94:"Helinox is advertising the Zero as being very similar to the One but at a much lighter weight.";i:33;s:42:"The material on the Zero has been changed.";i:34;s:49:"It utilizes a different and lighter chair fabric.";i:35;s:129:"Helinox have been working away at hiking chairs for a while so without further ado lets see how the Helinox Chair Zero stacks up.";i:36;s:163:"Weight Capacity Weighing in with a packed weight of 510 grams the Chair Zero is the lightest chair Helinox produces and one of the lightest of the foldable chairs.";i:37;s:38:"Check out the Helinox Chair Zero here.";i:38;s:122:"The Helinox Chair Zero weighs a mere 16-ounces and packs down to the size of a 32 ounce water bottle 138 x 39 x 39 inches.";i:39;s:143:"Praised for a compact featherweight the Chair Zero is super rugged thanks to the anodized DAC aluminum poles and ripstop polyester seat fabric.";i:40;s:19:"Helinox Chair Zero.";i:41;s:155:"The Helinox Chair Zero is a much-celebrated backpacking chair that has earned a near-legendary reputation for balancing low weight with reasonable comfort.";i:42;s:151:"With all of the hype surrounding the Chair Zero we here at Divein felt obligated to run it through the gauntlet to see if it lives up to the notoriety.";i:43;s:30:"Field Test Helinox Chair Zero.";i:44;s:89:"A few years ago I was leading a hike through the Lerderderg State Park in Victorias west.";i:45;s:129:"We stopped for lunch on a shady creek bed and as usual everyone searched for a comfortable log or rock to sit on or rest against.";i:46;s:165:"When it comes to breathability Helinox Chair One is the clear winner it features a very high ratio of mesh at the back and sides to let a fine breeze coming through.";i:47;s:121:"Helinox Chair Zero on the other hand features only two small holes at each corner for breathability and weight reduction.";i:48;s:60:"Both chairs feature high-strength fiber-reinforced Nylon 66.";i:49;s:101:"Chair Zeros frame is built with ultra-lightweight and exceptionally strong DAC aluminium alloy poles.";i:50;s:154:"This advanced pole technology was developed for expedition-level backpacking tents and is trusted and relied on by the worlds most discerning adventurers.";i:51;s:47:"Chair Zero is perfect for carrying on two feet.";i:52;s:46:"Its the lightest portable chair Helinox makes.";i:53;s:141:"The trade-off is some comfort the seat lacks the mesh ventilation panels of Chair One and some people find it a little tight around the hips.";i:54;s:65:"Chair Zero also sits a little lower to the ground than Chair One.";i:55;s:36:"If you dont mind carrying the extra.";i:56;s:98:"The Helinox beach chair is slightly wider than chair one or chair zero and the backrest is higher.";i:57;s:54:"So we sit very relaxed and with our head leaning back.";i:58;s:48:"This was the decisive argument for us to buy it.";i:59;s:58:"With the Helinox beach chair we sit just above the ground.";i:60;s:60:"Since we are camping and our camping stove is on the ground.";i:61;s:118:"The Helinox Zero is visually identical to the Helinox One but it weighs about half as much 11 lbs vs 2 lbs on the One.";i:62;s:95:"The Zero uses a different kind of fabric for the chair and is also slightly smaller when setup.";i:63;s:88:"Its a couple of inches closer to the ground and the seat bottom is a little bit smaller.";i:64;s:124:"Say hello to the Chair Zero from Helinox your new lightweight staple for relaxing on when space and weight are at a premium.";i:65;s:215:"Providing the comfort of a full-sized chair at the weight of a drink bottle the Chair Zero from Helinox is perfect for hikers paddlers or motorcycle tourers looking for a premium compact seating solution out in the.";i:66;s:159:"The Chair Zero is their lightest in the range 510 grams beating out the Ground Chair which looks smaller and more compact but in reality comes in at 640 grams.";i:67;s:105:"Adding just over 12 kilo to your pack to get a comfortable seat definitely requires a conscious decision.";i:68;s:74:"The Helinox Chair Zero is constructed using DAC Brand aluminium poles for.";}}